# Robustness Checks

| Robustness Test | Finding |
|-----------------|---------|
| Rolling window (10-year) | Results unchanged |
| Rolling window (20-year) | Results unchanged |
| Quarterly horizon | No improvement |
| Annual horizon | Slight improvement for some, but still generally negative |
| Different starting dates | Results robust |
| Alternative benchmarks | Historical average still wins |
| Equal-weighted combination | Underperforms |
| Principal components | Underperforms |

**Bottom line:** Results are robust across all sensible specification choices.

