# Limitations

| Category | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| **Time period** | Study ends in 2005; post-2008 financial crisis behavior not captured |
| **Transaction costs** | Does not account for trading costs of implementing forecasts |
| **International markets** | U.S. equity market only; may not generalize |
| **Nonlinear models** | Does not test machine learning or nonlinear approaches |
| **Real-time data** | Uses final revised data; real-time data vintages might differ |

